## Spacing Guidelines
- Use consistent spacing: `gap-2`, `gap-4`, `gap-6`, `gap-8`
- Use consistent padding: `p-2`, `p-4`, `p-6`, `px-4`, `py-2`
- Use consistent margins: `mb-4`, `mt-6`, `mx-2`
- Border radius: `rounded-md` (default), `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`